comment: * Listener interface for ActionBar navigation events. * * @deprecated Action bar navigation modes are deprecated and not supported by inline * toolbar action bars. Consider using other * common * navigation patterns instead.

methods.name: public boolean onNavigationItemSelected(int itemPosition, long itemId)
methods.comment:
* This method is called whenever a navigation item in your action bar
         * is selected.
         *    
         * @param itemPosition Position of the item clicked.
         * @param itemId ID of the item clicked.
         * @return True if the event was handled, false otherwise.

methodNames: public boolean onNavigationItemSelected(int itemPosition, long itemId)
